                    <p>Dear <t t-out="object.payroll_head_id.name"/>,</p>

                    <p>
                        IT Asset Clearance and Admin Clearance for
                        <b><t t-out="object.employee_id.name"/></b> have been successfully approved.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        You may now proceed with the Payroll Clearance process.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Regards,<br/>
                        <t t-out="object.admin_head_id.name"/>
                    </p>

